Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:02.67,Latin,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:06.43,Latin,,0,0,0,,welcome to soteriology.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:10.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,This course deals with the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:14.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,and the doctrine of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:17.43,Latin,,0,0,0,,how the Holy Spirit works in the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:20.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,Running all the way from His effectual calling,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:23.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,and regeneration,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:26.21,Latin,,0,0,0,,all the way to glorification.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:30.03,Latin,,0,0,0,,So it's a very important subject
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:33.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,and I'm glad you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:37.52,Latin,,0,0,0,,We're going to look at it in some detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:41.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,I think you'll enjoy the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:44.14,Latin,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:46.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,all of our
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:48.92,Latin,,0,0,0,,Christianity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:51.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,all of our personal religion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:55.44,Latin,,0,0,0,,is just a sham without the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:57.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,So we're very,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:01.93,Latin,,0,0,0,,very grateful for the ministry of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.97,Latin,,0,0,0,,I want to begin this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:09.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,first lecture with the reading of God's word,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:12.60,Latin,,0,0,0,,as we will with each each lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.02,Latin,,0,0,0,,Turn with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:17.23,Latin,,0,0,0,,please,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:22.14,Latin,,0,0,0,,to Romans 8 and I'll read 13 through 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:26.59,Latin,,0,0,0,,Romans 8: 13 through 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:28.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,For,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:31.54,Latin,,0,0,0,,if you live after the flesh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.14,0:01:34.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,you shall die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:36.59,Latin,,0,0,0,,But if ye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:39.14,Latin,,0,0,0,,through the Spirit do mortify,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:41.63,Latin,,0,0,0,,the deeds of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:44.33,Latin,,0,0,0,,ye shall live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:47.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,For as many as are led
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:50.14,Latin,,0,0,0,,by the Spirit of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.14,Latin,,0,0,0,,they are the sons of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.73,Latin,,0,0,0,,For you have not received the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:59.07,Latin,,0,0,0,,of bondage again to fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:02.18,Latin,,0,0,0,,but you have received the Spirit of adoption
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.77,Latin,,0,0,0,,whereby we cry Abba,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:09.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:13.44,Latin,,0,0,0,,The Spirit itself beareth witness with our spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.00,Latin,,0,0,0,,that we are the children of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:20.13,Latin,,0,0,0,,and if children then heirs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:23.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,heirs of God and joint heirs with Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:26.02,Latin,,0,0,0,,If so be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:28.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,that we suffer with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,that we may also be glorified together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:37.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,Let's seek God's face in prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.07,Latin,,0,0,0,,Lord God,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:44.24,Latin,,0,0,0,,we stand on holy ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,as we approach this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:51.73,Latin,,0,0,0,,immense subject of the third person of the Holy Trinity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,and his salvific work in our souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:03:00.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,And we do pray that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.19,Latin,,0,0,0,,by the end of this course,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:06.49,Latin,,0,0,0,,we will have a much more profound appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,for the saving ministry of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:14.46,Latin,,0,0,0,,than we perhaps might have at present
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:17.97,Latin,,0,0,0,,Help us to grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:21.73,Latin,,0,0,0,,not only in the grace and knowledge of Jesus,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:25.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,whom the Spirit focuses upon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:28.57,Latin,,0,0,0,,but also that we would grow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.25,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the grace and knowledge of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,becoming more aware of His work,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,His saving work,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.81,Latin,,0,0,0,,and appreciating more profoundly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:44.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,the vastness of His ministry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:48.18,Latin,,0,0,0,,as he works in sinners and rebels,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:51.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,such as we all are by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:55.65,Latin,,0,0,0,,So Lord bless this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:58.52,Latin,,0,0,0,,Help me in teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:01.73,Latin,,0,0,0,,Help the students in listening,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,learning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:07.49,Latin,,0,0,0,,and grant that each lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,may serve to thy glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:13.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,to our spiritual growth,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:15.79,Latin,,0,0,0,,and to the well-being
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:19.11,Latin,,0,0,0,,of our entire being as we journey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:22.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,to the never-ending eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.60,Latin,,0,0,0,,Be with us now we pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:28.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,In Jesus name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.72,Latin,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,thank you for joining us for this class
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:39.03,Latin,,0,0,0,,and I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.24,Latin,,0,0,0,,begin with the first lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.75,Latin,,0,0,0,,which is titled: The Study
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:48.07,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:51.37,Latin,,0,0,0,,The Study of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:57.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,God's Holy spirit was with God's people from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:02.36,Latin,,0,0,0,,Already in Genesis 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:04.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,verse 2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:08.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,leading them ultimately to their rest
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:15.57,Latin,,0,0,0,,in Jesus Christ (Isaiah 63 14)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:19.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,To know the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:23.11,Latin,,0,0,0,,therefore is to stand in continuity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.48,Latin,,0,0,0,,with the Saints of all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:30.21,Latin,,0,0,0,,God has promised,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:33.04,Latin,,0,0,0,,his Spirit already to Israel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.88,Latin,,0,0,0,,His chosen people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.65,Latin,,0,0,0,,We know that in the Old Testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:43.91,Latin,,0,0,0,,various individuals experience a comfort of that Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.37,Latin,,0,0,0,,Think of David,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:51.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,for example (Psalm 51)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.10,Latin,,0,0,0,,But God promised
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:57.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,a far richer and broader work of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:01.55,Latin,,0,0,0,,than we might possibly imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:05.79,Latin,,0,0,0,,Isaiah foretold of a righteous king
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,whose administration would be like,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:12.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,rivers of waters in a dry place
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,and the transformation of the barren wilderness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:21.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,into a world filled with the fruit of righteousness (Isaiah 32).
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,When the Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.61,Latin,,0,0,0,,When the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,is poured out upon us from on high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:34.65,Latin,,0,0,0,,And then he goes on to say in Isaiah 44,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:38.34,Latin,,0,0,0,,that the Spirit would be poured out on Israel,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,like a river
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:44.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,of water on dry ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,irrigating faithless souls to produce a people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:51.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,who say I am the Lord's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:55.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,And so the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:59.12,Latin,,0,0,0,,is the answer of God's covenantal faithfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,to the chronic problem
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.70,Latin,,0,0,0,,of Israel's covenant breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:08.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,You find that also in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.30,Latin,,0,0,0,,the Book of Joel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,that the Lord would pour out his Spirit upon all his people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.98,Latin,,0,0,0,,that whosoever would call on the name
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.36,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Lord would be saved
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:25.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,(Joel 2:28 to 32).
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:29.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,So to study the work of the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.30,Latin,,0,0,0,,is to study heavenly work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.33,Latin,,0,0,0,,saving work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:40.02,Latin,,0,0,0,,And work that abides forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:42.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:44.47,Latin,,0,0,0,,of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.98,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the New Testament age you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:51.77,Latin,,0,0,0,,that when Jesus rose from the dead
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:54.67,Latin,,0,0,0,,and ascended into heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.27,Latin,,0,0,0,,He poured out His Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,in much larger measures than
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:04.14,Latin,,0,0,0,,had previously been known
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:08.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,(Acts 2 17,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:12.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,through 21 and 33 and 34)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,And Peter after his sermon is interrupted by
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:22.04,Latin,,0,0,0,,thousands of people who are under great conviction of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:25.12,Latin,,0,0,0,,Under it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:28.48,Latin,,0,0,0,,and they cried out men and Brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:34.19,Latin,,0,0,0,,Peter said to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:37.60,Latin,,0,0,0,,repent and be baptized everyone of you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the name of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:44.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,And you shall receive the gift of the Holy Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.52,Latin,,0,0,0,,For the promise is unto you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.07,Latin,,0,0,0,,and to your children
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:53.18,Latin,,0,0,0,,and to all that are afar off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.43,Latin,,0,0,0,,Even as many as the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:09:01.93,Latin,,0,0,0,,Our God shall call (Acts 2: 38 and 39).
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.90,Latin,,0,0,0,,And so the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.73,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the New Testament writings,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,particularly Paul's Epistles,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,are just filled with the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:17.61,Latin,,0,0,0,,He speaks often
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:20.03,Latin,,0,0,0,,about being born
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Spirit such as Galatians,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,4: 29.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.59,Latin,,0,0,0,,And he's talking constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.52,Latin,,0,0,0,,about different aspects
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:35.42,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Spirit's saving work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.81,Latin,,0,0,0,,Like we just read a few
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.44,Latin,,0,0,0,,of them to you from from Romans 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:46.33,Latin,,0,0,0,,So if we treasure Christ as our only mediator,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:50.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,we will also treasure the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:53.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,as Christ's great gift,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:55.72,Latin,,0,0,0,,which is inseparable from Him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:59.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,to sinners (John 4
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.75,Latin,,0,0,0,,and again John 7).
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:07.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,Jonathan Edwards put it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:10.99,Latin,,0,0,0,,"The sum of the blessings Christ sought
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:14.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,by what he did and suffered
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the work of redemption,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,was the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:23.11,Latin,,0,0,0,,the Holy Spirit in His indwelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.25,Latin,,0,0,0,,His influences and fruits
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,is the sum of all grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:31.50,Latin,,0,0,0,,holiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,comfort and joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:37.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,or in one word
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:40.65,Latin,,0,0,0,,of all the spiritual good Christ purchased
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,for men in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.53,Latin,,0,0,0,,And is also the sum of all perfection,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.64,Latin,,0,0,0,,and eternal joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.92,Latin,,0,0,0,,that he purchased
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:57.14,Latin,,0,0,0,,for them in another world."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,That's an amazing quote by Edwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:04.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,And it certainly shows us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:08.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,that many today are minimizing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:11.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,the role of the ministry
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:13.70,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Holy Spirit as
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,integral with the entire
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.75,Latin,,0,0,0,,sum of blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:23.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,that God's people receive in salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:26.79,Latin,,0,0,0,,John Brown of Headington
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:29.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,put it this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:33.25,Latin,,0,0,0,,"Did Christ purchase the Holy Spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.94,Latin,,0,0,0,,Christ purchased the Spirit's gifts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:40.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,and influences in applying redemption,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:43.49,Latin,,0,0,0,,but not his being,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,which is independent."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,So the work of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,in many ways
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:54.44,Latin,,0,0,0,,is the fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,of Christ's death and resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:11:59.91,Latin,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.30,Latin,,0,0,0,,salvation in Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:06.47,Latin,,0,0,0,,is appreciated and enjoyed therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,only by knowing the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:12.44,Latin,,0,0,0,,and his saving work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.65,Latin,,0,0,0,,And this is one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.86,Latin,,0,0,0,,greatest doctrines of the Reformation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:22.21,Latin,,0,0,0,,developed so thoroughly and then even
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,augmented by the Puritans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:30.13,Latin,,0,0,0,,What a treasure Reformed theology brings us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:35.13,Latin,,0,0,0,,about the saving ministry of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.62,Latin,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.97,Latin,,0,0,0,,BB Warfield called John Calvin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:43.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,The Theologian of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:47.21,Latin,,0,0,0,,And Warfield went on to claim
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.25,Latin,,0,0,0,,the developed doctrine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:52.94,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the work of the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:56.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,is an exclusively Reformation doctrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.98,Latin,,0,0,0,,and more particularly a Reformed doctrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:04.42,Latin,,0,0,0,,and still more particularly a Puritan doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:06.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:09.62,Latin,,0,0,0,,study of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:13.93,Latin,,0,0,0,,through Reformed experiential soteriology,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.36,Latin,,0,0,0,,- that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.54,Latin,,0,0,0,,salvation that we experience
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:22.07,Latin,,0,0,0,,by the work
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.93,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Spirit in the soul -
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:28.37,Latin,,0,0,0,,opens up a vast wealth of wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,and joy to the believer.

